HI how do i resubmit rejected ads?

Hey there! If your ad got rejected, you should have received an email with the subject line ‘Urgent: Ad Rejected - Action Required.’ Check the email for the specific reason why your ad was rejected. Once you've addressed the issue (like resizing an image or revising a headline), you can resubmit your ad by saving it again. If you need more details, you can refer to this article: [My ad got rejected. What's next?](https://help.newsbreak.com/hc/en-us/articles/18085960681101-My-ad-got-rejected-What-s-next).
